			<div id="page_head"><span style="width: 100%;"><a id="skip_menu"></a></span>
				<h1>Russian Federation: Legal Aspects of War in Georgia</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="box_img"><img src="/web/20140716042951im_/http://www.loc.gov/law/images/header_help.jpg" alt="Law Library Stacks"/></div>
			<div id="main_nav"><a href="/web/20140716042951/http://www.loc.gov/law/help/">
				Research &amp; Reports
				</a> |
